title: Move text preparation and packing to a separate preprocessed step
message:
Move text preparation and packing to a separate preprocessed step

- Move the raw OCR files under imagery/txt
- Add script imagery/05_mk_txt.sh that runs stand-alone Java code
- TextPrepare.java: pre-process OCR files and pack them into txt.bin
- The app code itself (TextData) loads text data from this bin,
  which also yields a markable reduction in the app launch time.

title: Compound word search works via preprocessing the OCR text.
message:
Compound word search works via preprocessing the OCR text.

However, this preprocessing apparently works only on the host but not
the device (at the moment, at least). It might be a good idea to do
this preprocessing at compile-time anyway, compared to doing it each
time the app is started. This needs more work.
